0will%20start%20selling%20mifepristone%20in%20some%20US%20states%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20move%20follows%20a%202023%20FDA%20decision%20to%20allow%20certified%20pharmacies%20to%20sell%20the%20abortion%20drug.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20has%20supported%20increased%20access%20to%20abortion%2C%20hailed%20the%20news.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECVS%20and%20Walgreens%20are%20set%20to%20begin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fcvs-walgreens-begin-dispensing-abortion-pill-this-month-nyt-2024-03-01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eselling%20the%20abortion%20pill%20mifepristone%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20some%20states%20this%20month%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20(FDA)%20announced%20last%20year%20that%20it%20would%20allow%20retail%20pharmacies%20to%20begin%20selling%20the%20drug.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalgreens%20said%20it%20would%20roll%20out%20the%20drug%20in%20stores%20in%20New%20York%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Massachusetts%2C%20California%2C%20and%20Illinois%2C%20while%20CVS%20would%20first%20dispense%20the%20drug%20in%20Massachusetts%20and%20Rhode%20Island%2C%20the%20Reuters%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupporters%20say%20the%20medication%2C%20which%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20FDA%20in%202000%2C%20has%20a%20safe%20and%20effective%20record%20and%20that%20it%20carries%20no%20risk%20of%20overdose%20or%20addiction%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20groups%20like%20the%20Alliance%20for%20Hippocratic%20Medicine%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20its%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guttmacher.org%2Farticle%2F2022%2F02%2Fmedication-abortion-now-accounts-more-half-all-us-abortions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGuttmacher%20Institute%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20NGO%20that%20aims%20to%20improve%20sexual%20health%2C%20said%20that%20