3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERafale%20manufacturer%20Dassault%20Aviation%20%26quot%3Bregularly%20makes%20a%20selling%20point%20of%20its%20ability%20to%20begin%20delivering%20Rafale%20combat%20aircraft%20to%20prospective%20customers%20just%20three%20years%20from%20contract%20signature%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iiss.org%2Fonline-analysis%2Fmilitary-balance%2F2024%2F01%2Fdassaults-whirlwind-of-rafale-orders-may-be-too-much-of-a-good-thing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20International%20Institute%20for%20Strategic%20Studies.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20company's%20recent%20flurry%20of%20Rafale%20sales%20could%20make%20that%2036-month%20commitment%20more%20challenging%20and%20may%20even%20jeopardize%20some%20future%20deals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dassault-aviation.com%2Fen%2Fdefense%2Frafale%2Fintroduction%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERafale%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(%26quot%3BSquall%26quot%3B)%20is%20flown%2C%20or%20has%20been%20ordered%20by%2C%20eight%20nations%3A%20Egypt%2C%20Greece%2C%20India%2C%20Qatar%2C%20Croatia%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20and%20Indonesia%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20French%20Air%20Force%20and%20Navy.%20The%20jet%20first%20flew%20in%201986%2C%20and%20is%20considered%20a%20generation%204.5%20fighter%2C%20with%20some%20advanced%20features%20such%20as%20limited%20stealth%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20supercruise%20(fly%20supersonic%20without%20using%20fuel-guzzling%20afterburners)%2C%20and%20the%20capability%20to%20launch%20long-range%20missiles%20such%20as%20the%20Meteor%20and%20Mica.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrance%20has%20bought%20234%20Rafales%2C%20and%20in%20addition%2C%20another%20261%20have%20been%20ordered%20by%20various%20nations%2C%20according%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fair%2F2024%2F01%2F12%2Ffrance-buys-42-rafale-jets-for-more-than-55-billion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDefense%20News%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20question%20is%20whether%20Dassault%20can%20meet%20the%20demand.%20IISS%20calculates%20Dassault's%20production%20backlog%20at%20228%20aircraft.%20The%20crunch%20will%20be%20particularly%20acute%20between%202026%20to%202033%2C%20when%20Dassault%20will%20need%20to%20deliver%20174%20Rafales%20to%20France%2C%2042%20to%20Indonesia%2C%2080%20to%20the%20UAE%20and%2010%20for%20Egypt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20French%20aircraft%20maker%20aimed%20to%20produce%2015%20Rafales%20last%20year%20but%20only%20completed%2013%2C%26quot%3B%20IISS%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20company%20has%20not%20yet%20given%202024%20production%20guidance%2C%20though%20output%20will%20likely%20increase%20this%20year%20and%20next%2C%20given%20the%20strong%20demand.%20Even%20so%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20annual%20aircraft%20numbers%20will%20quickly%20reach%20mid-20s.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Dassault%20production%20averages%2020%20Rafales%20per%20year%20across%20both%202024%20and%202025%2C%20it%20leaves%20188%20aircraft%20to%20be%20delivered%20between%202026%20and%202033.%20This%20would%20necessitate%20a%20delivery%20rate%20of%20almost%2024%20aircraft%20per%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDifficulties%20manufacturing%20modern%20fighters%20are%20hardly%20unique%20to%20Dassault.%20In%201944%2C%20at%20Ford's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehenryford.org%2Fcollections-and-research%2Fdigital-collections%2Fexpert-sets%2F101765%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWillow%20Run%2C%20Michigan%20factory%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20four-engine%20B-24%20Liberator%20heavy%20bomber%20rolled%20off%20the%20production%20line%20every%2063%20minutes.%20In%202024%2C%20Lockheed%20Martin%20is%20struggling%20to%20deliver%20around%20a%20hundred%20F-35s%20this%20year%2C%20with%20each%20stealth%20fighter%20requiring%20around%2040%2C000%20labor%20hours%20to%20complete.%20Not%20only%20are%20today's%20aircraft%20more%20complicated%20to%20build%2C%20but%20they%20also%20comprise%20huge%20numbers%20of%20components%20often%20spread%20across%20global%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20F-35%20does%20have%20the%20advantage%20of%20being%20a%20global%20fighter%20manufactured%20by%20several%20nations%2C%20while%20the%20Rafale%20is%20a%20national%20fighter%20limited%20by%20French%20resources%2C%20argued%20aviation%20analyst%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frichardaboulafia.com%2Fseptember-2023-letter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERichard%20Aboulafia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20September.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Navy%20aircraft%20carrier%20Charles%20De%20Gaulle%20Dassault%20Rafale%20M%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e6261a7fee23d0f735ec7a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22932%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20French%20Dassault%20Rafale%20M%20fighter%20jet%20launches%20from%20the%20French%20aircraft%20carrier%20Charles%20De%20Gaulle%20during%20interoperability%20exercises%20with%20the%20aircraft%20carrier%20USS%20Dwight%20D.%20Eisenhower%2C%20March%203%2C%202020.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%2FMCS%202nd%20Class%20Kaleb%20J.%20Sarten%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Dassault%20can%20take%20some%20steps%20such%20as%20switching%20civilian%20aircraft%20production%20to%20Rafales%2C%20bottlenecks%20are%20likely%20to%20remain.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20Dassault%20relies%20heavily%20on%20a%20domestic%20supply%20chain%20for%20Rafale%20that%20insulates%20it%20somewhat%20from%20global%20supply-chain%20snarls%2C%20the%20company%20and%20its%20suppliers%20are%20not%20immune%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20IISS%20noted.%20%26quot%3BEngineering-talent%20shortages%20could%20also%20derail%20a%20sharp%20increase%20in%20Rafale%20manufacturing.%20Realistically%2C%20the%20Rafale%20industrial%20machine%20would%20be%20challenged%20to%20more%20than%20double%20its%20annual%20output.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENor%20are%20sporadic%20deliveries%20of%20a%20couple%20of%20Rafales%20here%20and%20there%20an%20option.%20%26quot%3BMost%20new%20customers%20placing%20a%20sizeable%20contract%20would%20want%20a%20delivery%20rate%20of%20at%20least%20six%20aircraft%20per%20year%20in%20order%20to%20train%20coherent%20groups%20of%20air%20and%20ground%20crew%20and%20build%20up%20full%20squadrons%20at%20a%20sensible%20rate%20%E2%80%94%20and%20achieving%20those%20numbers%20may%20be%20a%20hurdle%20too%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20IISS%20warned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20sales%20of%20the%20Rafale%20have%20been%20lackluster.%20But%20many%20nations%20are%20beefing%20up%20their%20air%20forces%2C%20even%20as%20Lockheed%20Martin%20has%20its%20hands%20full%20making%20enough%20F-35s%2C%20Russia%20is%20busy%20trying%20to%20replace%20aircraft%20losses%20from%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20despite%20Western%20sanctions%2C%20and%20many%20nations%20are%20hesitant%20to%20buy%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2021%2F06%2F30%2Fchina-fighter-jets-aircraft-exports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChinese%20jets%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20which%20is%20a%20plus%20for%20the%20Rafale.%20In%20a%20world%20where%20fighter%20sales%20have%20been%20dominated%20by%20US%20and%20Russian%20designs%20since%20World%20War%20II%2C%20French%20jets%20have%20offered%20customers%20an%20alternative.%20In%20the%201960s%20and%201970s%2C%20Dassault's%20agile%20delta-winged%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.militaryfactory.com%2Faircraft%2Fdetail.php%3Faircraft_id%3D228%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMirages%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20proved%20highly%20effective%20when%20flown%20by%20air%20forces%20such%20as%20Israel's.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20the%20Rafale%20is%20an%20option%20for%20nations%20that%20don't%20want%20the%20political%20and%20economic%20baggage%20that%20comes%20with%20buying%20American%20and%20Russian%20aircraft%20such%20as%20the%20F-35%2C%20F-16%2C%20and%20Su-35.%20Or%2C%20don't%20want%20to%20depend%20on%20a%20single%20nation%20to%20provide%20jets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20helps%20explain%20why%20the%20Rafale%20has%20become%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ainonline.com%2Faviation-news%2Fdefense%2F2023-11-07%2Fdassault-rafale-gulf-regions-best-selling-fighter-jet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epopular%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20India%20and%20several%20Middle%20Eastern%20nations.%20But%20the%20downside%20for%20Rafale%20customers%20is%20that%20they%20are%20dependent%20on%20a%20single%20nation%20whose%20defense-industrial%20base%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2Feurope%2F20240119-macron-urges-french-defence-firms-to-boost-production-to-support-ukraine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealready%20struggling%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20supply%20Ukraine%20and%20replenish%20France's%20own%20military.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ETwitter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3