the%20service%20are%20going%20to%20come%20with%20a%20wholesale%20price%20tag%20of%20at%20least%20%2430%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20month.%20And%20that's%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20cost%20of%20actually%20building%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20maintaining%20the%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20still%20don't%20know%3A%20Why%20would%20someone%20pay%20%2450%20a%20month%20for%20this%3F%20And%20how%20many%20people%20do%20the%20service's%20owners%20think%20will%20sign%20up%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20have%20an%20answer%20to%20the%20second%20question%3A%20Murdoch%20predicted%20that%20the%20service%20would%20have%205%20million%20subscribers%20within%205%20years%20of%20its%20launch.%20For%20context%3A%20Charter%20and%20Comcast%2C%20the%20two%20biggest%20pay-TV%20services%20in%20the%20US%2C%20have%2014%20million%20subscribers.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-tv-fourth-biggest-pay-tv-cable-broadband-bundle-google-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20TV%2C%20which%20has%208%20million%20subscribers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20now%20the%20fourth-biggest%20pay-TV%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lachlan%20Murdoch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F607564b93e3fe7001882a457%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELachlan%20Murdoch%20said%20the%20new%20sports%20streamer%20is%20expected%20to%20have%205%20million%20subscribers%20within%20five%20years%20of%20launch.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FBrendan%20McDermid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20back%20to%20the%20main%20question%3A%20Who%20exactly%20wants%20to%20pay%20for%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20if%20you%20like%20paying%20for%20streaming%20TV%2C%20you%20can%20pay%20%2473%20a%20month%20for%20YouTube%20TV.%20And%20YouTube%20TV%2C%20unlike%20the%20new%20sports%20streaming%20service%2C%20has%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20sports%20on%20TV.%20And%20the%20new%20streamer%20will%20only%20have%20%3Cem%3Esome%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20sports%20on%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20crucially%2C%20the%20new%20streamer%20won't%20have%20the%20NFL%20games%20broadcast%20by%20CBS%2C%20which%20has%20the%20contract%20for%20the%20league's%20AFC%20games%2C%20or%20NBC%2C%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fmost-watched-shows-2023-ncis-oscars-blue-bloods-super-bowl-yellowstone-1235854795%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESunday%20night%20NFL%20broadcasts%20are%20usually%20the%20most%20popular%20thing%20on%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20period.%20(Like%20YouTube%20TV%20and%20every%20other%20pay-TV%20service%2C%20it%20also%20won't%20have%20the%20Thursday%20night%20games%20now%20owned%20by%20Amazon%2C%20which%20used%20to%20get%20meh%20ratings%20but%20are%20now%20doing%20well%2C%20too.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20people%20like%20to%20say%20that%20sports%20is%20the%20key%20thing%20keeping%20the%20live%20TV%20business%20alive%2C%20what%20they%20really%20mean%20is%20NFL%20games.%20Every%20other%20sport%20on%20TV%20is%20a%20distant%20second%20place%20at%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20again%3A%20If%20you're%20a%20big%20enough%20sports%20fan%20that%20you%20want%20to%20pay%20for%20streaming%20TV%2C%20don't%20you%20also%20want%20%3Cem%3Eall%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20sports%20on%20streaming%20TV%3F%20Especially%20the%20most%20popular%20one%3F%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBecause%20regular%20TV%20can%20give%20you%20that%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20lots%20of%20other%20channels%20that%20won't%20be%20in%20this%20bundle%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20question%20that's%20befuddled%20me%20since%20this%20thing%20was%20announced.%20And%20when%20I%20talk%20to%20people%20in%20the%20industry%20about%20it%2C%20they're%20baffled%2C%20too.%20They're%20constantly%20offering%20up%20alternate%20theories%20about%20why%20this%20thing%20was%20put%20together%2C%20but%20none%20of%20them%20address%20the%20%26quot%3BSeriously%2C%20who's%20going%20to%20buy%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurdoch%20tried%20answering%20that%20Monday%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20tough%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20Murdoch%20has%20to%20do%20two%20things%3A%20He%20needs%20to%20convince%20himself%20and%20his%20investors%20that%20there's%20a%20large%20group%20of%20people%20who%20used%20to%20have%20pay%20TV%20but%20cut%20the%20cord%2C%20or%20never%20got%20pay%20TV%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20and%20would%20be%20interested%20in%20paying%20for%20this.%20And%20he%20also%20has%20to%20convince%20that%20same%20audience%20that%20this%20service%20%3Cem%3Ewon't%3C%2Fem%3E%20appeal%20to%20people%20who%20are%20already%20paying%20for%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20that%20it%20won't%20cannibalize%20his%20existing%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20answer%2C%20boiled%20down%3A%20Media%20consumers%20and%20analysts%20and%20investors%20who%20live%20on%20the%20coasts%20don't%20get%20it%2C%20but%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20living%20in%20middle%20America%20who%20would%20like%20to%20pay%20for%20sports%20on%20TV.%20They%20just%20don't%20want%20to%20spend%20so%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHuge%20number%20of%20households%20are%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoutside%20of%20the%20bundle%20%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20by%20which%20he%20means%20people%20who%20don't%20get%20the%20traditional%20pay%20TV%20packages%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bfor%20reasons%20other%20than%20that%20they%20don't%20love%20sports%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20are%20outside%20of%20the%20bundle%20that%20are%20still%20very%20strong%2C%20very%20passionate%20sports%20fans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20yes%3A%20Spending%20%2450%20a%20month%20on%20something%20instead%20of%20%2473%20a%20month%20on%20something%20is%20meaningfully%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20can%20also%20flip%20it%20around%3A%20The%20consumers%20Murdoch%20says%20he'll%20reach%20are%20theoretically%20not%20paying%20for%20TV%