n%20handed%20over%20an%20envelope%20to%20the%20governor%2C%20stating%20that%20he%20had%20brought%20a%20gift%20for%20him.%20The%20envelope%20contained%20a%20lock%20and%20a%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20then%2C%20asked%20the%20governor%20to%20lock%20the%20opposition%20inside%20the%20assembly%2C%20so%20that%20they%20could%20not%20%26quot%3Brun%20away%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20discussion%2C%20which%20later%20triggered%20a%20heated%20argument%20between%20LoP%20Bajwa%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Chandigarh%3A%20Amid%20the%20heated%20argument%20between%20Punjab%20CM%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20and%20Congress%20MLA%20and%20LoP%20Partap%20Singh%20Bajwa%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20CM%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20does%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20sit%20with%3F%20With%20me.%20Have%20you%20ever%20sat%20with%20them%3F%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20you%20are%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FxilZG9L5qM%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FxilZG9L5qM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1764587889352970311%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20agitated%20chief%20minister%20Mann%20asked%20Bajwa%20to%20tell%20the%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20Congress%20not%20to%20%26quot%3Bbother%26quot%3B%20giving%20seats%20to%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20does%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20sit%20with%3F%20With%20me.%20Have%20you%20ever%20sat%20with%20them%3F%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20you%20are%20making%20agreements%20(on%