of%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20in%20Geneva%2C%20Turk%20voiced%20concern%20by%20%26quot%3Bincreasing%20restrictions%20on%20the%20civic%20space%20%E2%80%93%20with%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20journalists%20and%20perceived%20critics%20targeted%20%E2%80%93%20as%20well%20as%20by%20hate%20speech%20and%20discrimination%20against%20minorities%2C%20especially%20Muslims.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20his%20concerns%20in%20this%20regard%20are%20unwarranted%20and%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20largest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Bagchi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bagchi%20underlined%20that%20in%20any%20democracy%2C%20%E2%80%9Cargumentation%20is%20natural.%20It%20is%20imperative%20that%20those%20in%20positions%20of%20authority%20do%20not%20allow%20their%20judgment%20to%20be%20clouded%20by%20propaganda.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20envoy%20added%20that%20India's%20electoral%20process%20has%20been%20characterised%20by%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20people's%20participation%20and%20full%20faith%20in%20the%20electoral%20mandate%20by%20all.%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20we%20are%20privileged%20that%20many%20across%20the%20world%20seek%20to%20learn%20from%20our%20experience%20and%20aspire%20to%20emulate%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20doubt%20that%20as%20in%20numerous%20occasions%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Indian%20people%20will%20freely%20exercise%20their%20vote%20to%20choose%20a%20government%20that%20they%20believe%20can%20best%20give%20voice%20and%20flight%20to%20their%20aspirations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Bagchi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20global%20update%2C%20Turk%20said%20that%20in%20India%2C%20with%20an%20electorate%20of%20960%20million%20people%2C%20the%20coming%20election%20will%20be%20unique%20in%20scale.%20%26quot%3BI%20appreciate%20the%20country's%20secular%20and%20democratic%20traditions%20and%20its%20great%20diversity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20head%20to%20the%20polls%20for%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20between%20April%20and%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurk%2C%20however%2C%20voiced%20concern%20about%20%26quot%3Bincreasing%20restrictions%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20civic%20space%20as%20well%20as%20by%20hate%20speech%20and%20discrimination%20against%20minorities%2C%20especially%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasised%20that%20it%20is%20particularly%20important%20in%20a%20pre-electoral%20context%20to%20ensure%20an%20open%20space%20that%20respects%20the%20meaningful%20participation%20of%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20welcomed%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20last%20month%20on%20campaign%20finance%20schemes%2C%20upholding%20the%20right%20to%20information%20and%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20ruled%20that%20electoral%20bonds%20violate%20citizens'%20right%20to%20access%20information%20held%20by%20the%20government%20and%20thus%20struck%20down%20the%20seven-year-old%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bagchi%20further%20said%20that%20plurality%2C%20diversity%2C%20inclusivity%2C%20and%20openness%20are%20at%20the%20core%20of%20India's%20democratic%20polity%20and%20its%20constitutional%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20backed%20by%20fiercely%20independent%20institutions%2C%20including%20a%20robust%20judiciary%2C%20that%20aims%20to%20protect%20the%20rights%20of%20all.%E2%80%9D%20He%20said%20that%20India%2C%20as%20home%20to%201%2F6%20of%20humanity%2C%20has%20led%20from%20the%20front%20with%20an%20enduring%20dedication%20to%20the%20promotion%20and%20protection%20of%20human%20rights%20for%20all.%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20endeavour%2C%20our%20approach%20has%20been%20guided%20by%20our%20civilisation%20ethos%20that%20views%20the%20world%20as%20one%20family.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20more%20recently%2C%20this%20commitment%20was%20manifest%20in%20India's%20response%20to%20the%20pandemic%20by%20assisting%20its%20friends%20and%20partners%20across%20the%20world%2C%20India's%20disaster%20relief%20efforts%20and%20support%20during%20crises%20in%20various%20countries%2C%20the%20development%20initiatives%20across%20the%20world%20and%20India's%20G20%20presidency%20last%20year%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhere%20we%20voiced%20particularly%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20Global%20South.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20when%20the%20world%20is%20riddled%20with%20conflicts%20and%20war%2C%20India%20has%20been%20a%20voice%20of%20reason%20consistently%20calling%20for%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy.%20It%20is%20only%20when%20peace%20is%20given%20a%20chance%20that%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20can%20hope%20for%20a%20better%20future%2C%20where%20their%20basic%20needs%20are%20met%2C%20and%20their%20human%20rights%20are%20protected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bagchi%20said%20that%20it%20is%20in%20this%20spirit%20that%20India%20welcomes%20the%20%E2%80%9Crenewed%20focus%20on%20issues%20affecting%20us%20all%2C%20such%20as%20reform%20of%20the%20multilateral%20governance%20structures%2C%20including%20international%20financial%20architecture%2C%20enhancing%20technical%20assistance%20and%20capacity%20building%2C%20sustainable%20development%20and%20the%20need%20for%20peace.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709574900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fneg61fe8_arindam-bagchi-un_625x300_04_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-strong-reply-after-un-rights-body-heads-electoral-process-remark-5175351%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20on%20Monday%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bconcerns%26quot%3B%20raised%20by%20the%20UN's%20top%20human%20rights%20official%20over%20its%20elector