al%20ties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Maldivian%20defence%20ministry%20posted%20on%20its%20X%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20of%20the%20defence%20cooperation%20agreement%20were%20not%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20China%20has%20also%20gifted%2012%20eco-friendly%20ambulances%20to%20Maldives%2C%20Edition.mv%20news%20portal%20reported%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20ceremony%20held%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Chinese%20Ambassador%20to%20Maldives%20Wang%20Lixin%20presented%20the%20letter%20gifting%20the%20ambulances%20to%20the%20Maldives%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visit%20of%20the%20Chinese%20military%20delegation%20took%20place%20days%20after%20Male%20allowed%20Xiang%20Yang%20Hong%2003%2C%20a%20hi-tech%20Chinese%20research%20ship%20to%20make%20a%20port%20call%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Brotation%20of%20its%20personnel%20and%20replenishment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%205%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20while%20denying%20entry%20to%20the%20same%20ship%2C%20said%20it%20has%20declared%20a%20moratorium%20on%20foreign%20research%20ships%20entering%20its%20waters%20for%20a%20year%20amid%20concerns%20from%20India%20over%20Chinese%20research%20vessels%20docking%20in%20its%20neighbourhood%20and%20collecting%20data%20from%20the%20oceans%2C%20including%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%2C%20for%20military%20purposes%2C%20especially%20for%20submarine%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20Foreign%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20has%20previously%20defended%20the%20port%20call%20by%20the%20Chinese%20research%20ship%20to%20the%20Maldives%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BChina's%20scientific%20research%20activities%20in%20relevant%20waters%20are%20for%20peaceful%20purposes%20and%20aimed%20at%20contributing%20to%20humanity's%20scientific%20understanding%20of%20the%20ocean.%26quot%3B%20The%20visit%20of%20the%20Chinese%20military%20delegation%20to%20the%20Maldives%20is%20taking%20place%20days%20after%20India%20confirmed%20that%20its%20first%20civilian%20team%20of%20technical%20experts%20has%20reached%20the%20island%20nation%20to%20replace%20the%20military%20personnel%20operating%20an%20advanced%20light%20helicopter%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Muizzu%2C%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20pro-China%20leader%2C%20has%20set%20March%2010%20as%20the%20deadline%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20first%20group%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20from%20his%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20team%20of%20technical%20personnel%20to%20operate%20the%20advanced%20light%20helicopter%20has%20reached%20the%20Maldives.%20It%20will%20replace%20the%20existing%20personnel%20who%20were%20operating%20this%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20in%20New%20Delhi%20at%20his%20weekly%20media%20briefing%20on%20February%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20meetings%20of%20the%20high-level%20core%20group%20that%20was%20set%20up%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20Indian%20military%20personnel%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20foreign%20ministry%20had%20said%20India%20will%20replace%20all%20its%20military%20personnel%20in%20two%20phases%20by%20May%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Maldivian%20government%2C%2088%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20are%20in%20the%20country%2C%20primarily%20to%20operate%20two%20helicopters%20and%20an%20aircraft%20that%20have%20carried%20out%20hundreds%20of%20medical%20evacuations%20and%20humanitarian%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20came%20under%20some%20strain%20since%20Muizzu%20came%20to%20power%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20maintained%20after%20assuming%20charge%20as%20the%20president%20that%20he%20would%20keep%20his%20election%20promise%20of%20evicting%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20from%20his%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20defeated%20India-friendly%20incumbent%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih%20in%20the%20presidential%20runoff%20held%20in%20September%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives%20is%20one%20of%20India's%20key%20maritime%20neighbours%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20and%20the%20overall%20bilateral%20ties%2C%20including%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20defence%20and%20security%2C%20witnessed%20an%20upward%20trajectory%20under%20the%20previous%20government%20in%20Male.%20The%20current%20government%20has%20said%20that%20it%20was%20reviewing%20more%20than%20100%20bilateral%20agreements%20signed%20with%20India%20by%20the%20previous%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives'%20proximity%20to%20India%2C%20barely%2070%20nautical%20miles%20from%20the%20island%20of%20Minicoy%20in%20Lakshadweep%20and%20300%20nautical%20miles%20from%20the%20mainland's%20western%20coast%2C%20and%20its%20location%20at%20the%20hub%20of%20commercial%20sea%20lanes%20running%20through%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20(IOR)%20gives%20it%20significant%20strategic%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709572380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fo6iheve8_mizzu-xi-jinping_625x300_04_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmaldives-to-get-free-military-assistance-from-china-amid-row-with-india-5176362%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20on%20Monday%20signed%20a%20defence%20cooperation%20agreement%20with%20the%20Maldives%20to%20provide%20free%20military%20assistance%20to%20foster%20%26quot%3Bstronger%26quot%3B%20bilateral%20ties%2C%20weeks%20after%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20set%20a%20deadline%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20first%20group%20of%20Indian%20mili%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%