FSL%20report%2C%20circumstantial%20evidence%2C%20witness%20statements%2C%20and%20available%20evidence%2C%20three%20individuals%20have%20been%20arrested.%20Legal%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20said%20the%20police%20have%20been%20given%20complete%20freedom%20to%20act%20in%20the%20case.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20given%20the%20police%20freedom%20to%20do%20everything%20in%20this%20case.%20And%20they%20have%20done%20their%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20state%20BJP%20chief%20BY%20Vijayendra%20said%20the%20arrest%20was%20a%20result%20of%20his%20party's%20relentless%20protests%20inside%20and%20outside%20the%20Vidhan%20Soudha.%20%26quot%3BThe%20protests%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20workers%20inside%20and%20outside%20Vidhana%20Soudha%20have%20borne%20fruit.%20We%20have%20now%20got%20information%20that%20three%20people%20have%20been%20arrested.%20They%20are%20traitors.%20I%20request%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20not%20to%20stop%20with%20their%20arrest.%20Justice%20doesn't%20end%20there.%20Who%20are%20these%20people%3F%20What%20is%20their%20background%3F%20Are%20more%20involved%3F%20Who%20permitted%20them%20to%20enter%20the%20Vidhana%20Soudha%3F%20Who%20instigated%20them%20to%20shout%20these%20slogans%3F%20All%20these%20need%20to%20be%20investigated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Mohammed%20Shafi's%20home%20in%20Karnataka's%20Haveri%2C%20there%20was%20an%20eerie%20silence.%20His%20family%20has%20locked%20themselves%20inside%20their%20home%20and%20turned%20off%20the%20lights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20her%20brother's%20arrest%2C%C2%A0Mohammed%20Shafi's%20sister%20broke%20down%20before%20journalists%20as%20she%20asserted%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20brother%20is%20not%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20THE%20CASE%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2027%2C%20soon%20after%20Nasir%20Hussain's%20victory%20march%20at%20the%20Vidhana%20Soudha%2C%20one%20of%20the%20media%20channels%20ran%20a%20video%20clip%20highlighting%20the%20%26quot%3Banti-national%26quot%3B%20slogans%20at%20the%20victory%20rally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20BJP%20attacked%20Congress%20over%20this%2C%20the%20ruling%20government%20in%20the%20state%20claimed%20necessary%20actions%20would%20be%20taken%20once%20the%20video%20and%20its%20audio%20were%20scientifically%20tested%20at%20the%20Forensic%20Science%20Lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Minister%20Priyank%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20private%20agency%20that%20analysed%20the%20video%20and%20audio%20confirmed%20that%20no%20slogans%20were%20raised%20in%20support%20of%20Pakistan.%20If%20the%20FSL%20report%20confirms%20the%20claims%2C%20we%20will%20take%20action.%20Let%20the%20report%20be%20released.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20audio%20and%20video%20clips%20were%20sent%20in%20for%20the%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20released%20an%20analysis%20of%20the%20audio%20and%20video%20by%20a%20private%20agency.%20The%20report%20claimed%20that%20it%20is%20highly%20probable%20that%20%26quot%3BPakistan%20Zindabad%26quot%3B%20slogans%20were%20indeed%20raised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20X%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20BJP%20claimed%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20scientific%20report%20revealed%20that%20the%20creators%20of%20fake%20news%20are%20the%20Congressmen%20who%20spread%20lies%20by%20distorting%20the%20truth.%20The%20FSL%20report%20revealed%20that%20%26quot%3BPakistan%20Zindabad%26quot%3B%20slogans%20in%20Vidhan%20Soudha%20were%20changed%20to%20%26quot%3BNasir%20Saab%20Zindabad%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20they%20tried%20to%20put%20a%20cap%20on%20the%20Kannadigas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20lashed%20out%20at%20Priyank%20Kharge%2C%20calling%20him%20%26quot%3Bthe%20head%20of%20the%20anti-national%20and%20fake%20news%20factory%26quot%3B.%20The%20Oppo