ket%20which%20had%20Tamil%20Nadu%20reeling%20at%2042%2F5%20inside%20the%20first%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20could%20never%20recover%20as%20they%20were%20shot%20out%20for%20paltry%20totals%20of%20146%20and%20162%20in%20the%20two%20innings%20as%20Mumbai%20stormed%20into%20the%20final%20for%20the%2048th%20time%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20moment%20I%20saw%20the%20wicket%20I%20exactly%20knew%20what%20we%20were%20going%20to%20get%2C%26quot%3B%20Kulkarni%20told%20the%20media%20here%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20saw%20that%20they%20had%20played%20on%20a%20different%20pitch%20in%20the%20quarterfinal%20and%20what%20wicket%20they%20gave%2C%20(that)%20moment%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20is%20a%20seaming-friendly%20wicket%20and%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20very%20tough%20match%2C%20we%20would%20have%20to%20play%20really%20well%20to%20win%20this%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20speak%20straightforward%20%E2%80%94%20we%20lost%20the%20match%20at%209'o%20clock%20on%20Day%20One.%20Everything%20was%20set%2C%20we%20won%20the%20toss%2C%20as%20a%20coach%2C%20as%20a%20Mumbaikar%2C%20I%20know%20the%20conditions%20well.%20We%20should%20have%20bowled%20but%20the%20captain%20had%20some%20different%20instinct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%20he%20is%20the%20boss.%20I%20can%20give%20my%20feedback%20and%20inputs%20(as%20to)%20what%20kind%20of%20wickets%20and%20Mumbai's%20mindset%20also.%20(From)%20106%2F7%2C%20I%20knew%20before%20the%20match%20that%20this%20(Mumbai's%20fightback)%20may%20happen.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKulkarni%20said%20Mumbai%20have%20the%20best%20lower-order%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20the%20best%20(Nos)%209%2C%2010%20(and)%20in%20India.%20I%20told%20this%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%20that%20their%20batting%20starts%20after%20(No)%206.%20I%20can%20take%20the%20horse%20to%20the%20water%2C%20the%20horse%20has%20to%20drink.%E2%80%9D%20Kulkarni%20said%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20plans%20were%20set%20for%20both%20outcomes%20of%20the%20coin%20toss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20mentally%20prepared%20that%20whoever%20wins%20the%20toss%20would%20bowl%20first.%20We%20knew%20that%20we%20would%20bowl%20first.%20The%20moment%20they%20(TV%20broadcast)%20said%20we%20would%20bat%20first%2C%20whatever%20you%20say%2C%20it%20goes%20in%20the%20batsmen's%20minds.%20That%20first%20half%20an%20hour%20(before%20play)%20got%20in%20the%20batsmen's%20minds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20get%20into%20the%20first%20over%2C%20third%20ball%2C%20your%20international%20player%20gets%20out%20and%20you%20see%20the%20situation%E2%80%A6%20in%20the%20first%20hour%20we%20lost%20the%20game%20and%20the%20plot.%20It%20was%20very%20difficult%20to%20come%20back%20even%20though%20they%20were%20107%20for%20seven%20(106%2F7).%26quot%3B%20Kulkarni%20said%20%E2%80%98instinctive'%20decision%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20skipper%20Sai%20Kishore%20has%20worked%20both%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgain%2C%20the%20instinctive%20decision%2C%20that%20inner%20voice%2C%20has%20played%20a%20big%20role.%20If%20you%20can%20say%20(it%20in)%20the%20positive%20way%2C%20the%20inner%20voice%20has%20helped%20also%20in%20reaching%20the%20semifinal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20previous%20match%20against%20Saurashtra%2C%20he%20went%20at%20No%203%20and%20scored%2065.%20That%20was%20again%20the%20inner%20voice%2C%20which%20has%20played%20(out)%20the%20positive%20way.%20Every%20captain%20has%20a%20different%20mindset%2C%20then%20I%20would%20say%20%E2%80%98why%20not%2C%20I%20won't%20blame%20the%20captain'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOther%20captains%20in%20the%20last%207-8%20years%20must%20have%20tried%20but%20they%20did%20not%20reach%20the%20semifinal.%20I%20looked%20at%20it%20from%20a%20positive%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BKishore%20can%20certainly%20take%20200%20wickets%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Mumbai%20player%20and%20coach%20however%20praised%20left-arm%20spinner%20Kishore%20as%20a%20prospect%20to%20take%20200%20wickets%20in%20Test%20cricket%20if%20given%20an%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20seen%20many%20left-arm%20spinners%20in%20last%20many%20years.%20As%20far%20as%20a%20left-arm%20spinner%20is%20concerned%2C%20he%20is%20a%20high%20quality%20bowler%20because%20he%20has%20all%20requisites%20to%20be%20a%20successful%20international%20player%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kulkarni%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20height%2C%20overspin%2C%20arm%20ball%2C%20and%20bounce%20like%20Jaddu%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F855-ravindra-jadeja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fa%3E).%20If%20you%20play%20on%20these%20kinds%20of%20wickets%2C%20the%20way%20India%20is%20playing%20currently%2C%20I%20think%20he%20can%20certainly%20take%20200%20wickets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKulkarni%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20backed%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajinkya%20Rahane%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F965-ajinkya-rahane-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAjinkya%20Rahane%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20lead%20Mumbai%20to%20their%2042nd%20title%20win%20in%20the%20final%20starting%20on%20March%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20Ajinkya%20Rahane.%20He%20has%20made%20a%20big%20difference%20to%20this%20team%20though%20he%20has%20not%20performed%20as%20a%20batter.%20But%20as%20leader%20he%20gelled%20with%20the%20team.%20He%20is%20like%20my%20student%20from%20U-15%20days%2C%20he%20was%20a%20successful%20captain%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20captained%20the%20team%20when%20things%20were%20not%20going%20in%20favour%20for%20India.%20He%20has%20handled%20the%20team%20in%20a%20way%20t