on%20Commission%2C%20news%20reports%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegal%20news%20site%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20bank%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsbi-requests-supreme-court-to-extend-time-till-june-30-to-furnish-electoral-bonds-information-251219%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Easked%20for%20time%20until%20June%2030%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%20citing%20difficulties%20in%20following%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20original%20deadline%20of%20March%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20SBI%20said%20that%2022%2C217%20bonds%20had%20been%20issued%20to%20various%20political%20parties%20between%20April%202019%20and%20February%2015%20this%20year%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20the%20period%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20specified%20in%20its%20order%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20redeemed%20bonds%20were%20gradually%20mailed%20by%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20authorised%20branches%20to%20its%20main%20branch%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20added%20that%20because%20there%20were%20two%20%E2%80%98information%20silos%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20had%20to%20compile%2044%2C434%20sets%20of%20information%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20was%20brought%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%20early%202018.%20Through%20it%2C%20companies%20and%20individuals%20in%20India%20could%20make%20anonymous%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20February%2015%20order%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20electoral%20bonds%20violated%20voters%E2%80%99%20fundamental%20right%20to%20information%20and%20ordered%20the%20SBI%20to%20stop%20issuing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20ordered%20the%20bank%20to%20furnish%20the%20details%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20purchased%20between%20an%20interim%20order%20it%20issued%20on%20April%2012%2C%202019%20and%20the%20date%20of%20its%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20details%20must%20include%20the%20date%20the%20bonds%20were%20purchased%20on%2C%20the%20names%20of%20who%20purchased%20them%20and%20the%20bonds%E2%80%99%20denominations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20ordered%20the%20bank%20to%20submit%20the%20details%20of%20bonds%20encashed%20by%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20concerned%20time%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelevant%20details%20must%20include%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20date%20of%20encashment%20and%20the%20denomination%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20was%20ordered%20to%20publish%20on%20its%20website%20by%20March%2013%20the%20information%20given%20to%20it%20by%20the%20SBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Fbiz-tech%2F2024%2F02%2F05%2Fsbi-issues-electoral-bonds-worth-rs-16518-crore-in-30-tranches.html%5C%22%3ERs%2016%2C518%20crore%20worth%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20sold%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%202018%20to%20the%20start%20of%202024%2C%20the%20government%20recently%20informed%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20reading%20out%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20said%20that%20financial%20contributions%20to%20political%20parties%20are%20made%20either%20to%20support%20them%20or%20in%20fulfilment%20of%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangements%2C%20referring%20to%20contributions%20being%20made%20in%20exchange%20for%20something%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20court%20stressed%20that%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20of%20political%20affiliation%20does%20not%20extend%20to%20contributions%20made%20to%20influence%20public%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709562401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04200200%2F3076973126_ab45efee1b_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fstate-bank-of-india-extra-time-june-30-electoral-bonds-supreme-court%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bank%20cited%20difficulties%20in%20following%20the%20court's%20original%20deadline%20of%20March%206%20and%20said%20it%20had%20to%20process%2044%2C434%20sets%20of%20information%20regarding%20bonds%20bought%20and%20encashed%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20LiveLaw%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fstate-bank-of-india-extra-time-june-30-electoral-bonds-supreme-court%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apeejay%20Surrendra%20Park%20Hotels%20Q3%20net%20profit%20rises%2046%20pc%20to%20Rs%2027.42%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709562400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2016-01%2F11%2Ffull%2F1452458588-3483.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fapeejay-surrendra-park-hotels-q3-net-profit-rises-46-pc-to-rs-27-42-cr-124030400944_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20had%20posted%20a%20consolidated%20net%20profit%20of%20Rs%2018.77%20crore%20in%20the%20same%20quarter%20last%20fiscal%2C%20the%20newly-listed%20firm%20said%20in%20a%20regulatory%20filing%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fapeejay-surrendra-park-hotels-q3-net-profit-rises-46-pc-to-rs-27-42-cr-124030400944_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fapeejay-surrendra-park-hotels-q3-net-profit-rises-46-pc-to-rs-27-42-cr-124030400944_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fapeejay-surrendra-park-hotels-q3-net-profit-rises-46-pc-to-rs-27-42-cr-124030400944_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SBI%20Requests%20Supreme%20Court%20To%20Extend%20Deadline%20To%20Give%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Info%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20has%20requested%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20extend%20the%20deadline%20till%20June%2030%20for%20giving%20information%20about%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20a%20historic%20judgment%20last%20month%20had%20struck%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20and%20told%20SBI%20to%20give%20the%20information%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20by%20March%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20ended%20the%20controversial%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20violated%20citizens'%20right%20to%20information.%20The%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20had%20said%2C%20was%20unconstitutional%20and%20arbitrary%20and%20may%20lead%20to%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangement%20between%20political%20parties%20and%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20ordered%20SBI%20to%20stop%20issuing%20these%20bonds%20and%20give%20details%20of%20donations%20made%20through%20this%20mode%20to%20the%20EC.%20The%20poll%20body%20was%20then%20told%20to%20publish%20this%20information%20on%20its%20website%20by%20March%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20bench%20of%20five%20judges%20held%20that%20the%20stated%20objective%20of%20fighting%20black%20money%20and%20maintaining%20the%20confidentiality%20of%20donors%20cannot%20defend%20the%20scheme.%20Electoral%20bonds%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20are%20not%20the%20only%20way%20to%20curb%20black%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20was%20introduced%20in%202018%20with%20the%20stated%20objective%20of%20blocking%20black%20money%20from%20entering%20the%20political%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20then%20Finance%20Minister%20Arun%20Jaitley%20had%20said%20the%20conventional%20practice%20of%20political%20funding%20in%20India%20was%20cash%20donations.%20%26quot%3BThe%20sources%20are%20anonymous%20or%20pseudonymous.%20The%20quantum%20of%20money%20was%20never%20disclosed.%20The%20present%20system%20ensures%20unclean%20money%20coming%20from%20unidentifiable%20sources.%20It%20is%20a%20wholly%20non-transparent%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%20On%20the%20confidentiality%20clause%2C%20he%20had%20said%20the%20disclosure%20of%20the%20donors'%20identity%20would%20make%20them%20go%20back%20to%20the%20cash%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20scheme%20was%20implemented%2C%20multiple%20parties%20challenged%20it%20in%20court.%20These%20included%20CPM%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Jaya%20Thakur%2C%20and%20the%20non-profit%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms.%20They%20argued%20that%20the%20confidentiality%20clause%20came%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20citizen's%20right%20to%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709561940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F2074em5g_rajasthan-assembly-elections-_625x300_11_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsbi-requests-supreme-court-to-extend-deadline-till-june-30-to-give-electoral-bonds-information-to-election-commission-5175191%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20has%20requested%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20extend%20the%20deadline%20till%20June%2030%20for%20giving%20information%20about%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsbi-requests-supreme-court-to-extend-deadline-till-june-30-to-give-electoral-bonds-information-to-election-commission-5175191%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Emraan%20is%20surprised%20with%20Kangana