20of%20concerns%20spanned%20the%20following%20issues%2C%20even%20if%20not%20fleshed%20out%20in%20so%20many%20details%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethat%2C%20in%20order%20to%20secure%2Frestore%20economic%20sanity%20to%20the%20realm%20and%20justice%20to%20disempowered%20masses%20at%20large%2C%C2%A0%20cronies%20and%20cronyism%20required%20to%20be%20held%20to%20account%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethe%20policy%20of%20privatisation%20that%20has%20taken%20mountains%20of%20public%20wealth%20away%20from%20the%20citizen%20needs%20to%20be%20recouped%20and%20channeled%20with%20equity%20and%20sustained%20social%20concern%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethat%20the%20embarrassingly%20yawning%2C%20indeed%2C%20record%20levels%20of%20economic%20inequality%20demand%20to%20be%20rectified%20by%20restoring%20and%20creating%20jobs%20and%20enhancing%C2%A0%20the%20purchasing%20power%20of%20the%20hoi%20polloi%20%C2%A0so%20that%20both%20objects%20of%20alleviating%20misery%20and%20enabling%20consumer%20investment%20are%20furthered%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethat%20state%20agencies%20cry%20to%20be%20returned%20to%20the%20autonomy%20%C2%A0%C2%A0marked%20for%20them%20by%20the%20constitutional%20scheme%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20a%20transparently%20just%20%C2%A0rule%20of%20law%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethat%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20especially%20that%20of%20the%20media%2C%20(now%20at%20161%20out%20of%20189%20internationally)%20cries%20to%20be%20reinstated%20to%20make%20the%20democratic%20%C2%A0boast%20of%20the%20republic%20credible%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethat%20policing%20and%20investigation%20scream%20to%20be%20unshackled%20from%20the%20contumely%20and%20influence%20of%20high%20office%20BS%20made%20demonstrably%20%C2%A0unbiased%20and%20%C2%A0fearlessly%20law-abiding%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20subjects%20of%20its%C2%A0%20enquiries%2C%20correcting%C2%A0%20a%20%C2%A0corroded%20%C2%A0%C2%A0pattern%20of%20functioning%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethat%20academic%20institutions%20and%20other%20watch-dog%20establishments%20need%20to%20be%20freed%20from%20enslavement%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethat%20the%20electoral%20system%20and%20its%20manifold%20operations%20need%20to%20be%20freed%20form%20pressures%20that%20often%20bring%20its%20activities%2Fdecisions%20into%20question%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethat%20criticism%20of%20t%20he%20government%20be%20recognised%20to%20be%20the%20%C2%A0essential%20ingredient%20of%20democratic%20%C2%A0philosophy%20and%20%C2%A0public%20%C2%A0culture%2C%20not%C2%A0%20to%20BE%20%C2%A0conflated%20with%20or%20mischievously%20projected%20as%20anti-state%20activity%E2%80%99%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethat%2C%20as%20per%20constitutional%20injunction%2C%20the%20state%20be%20brought%20back%20to%20regarding%20all%20religions%20in%20the%20realm%20with%20equal%C2%A0%20consideration%2C%20and%20refrain%20from%20patronising%20or%20maligning%20%C2%A0any%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethat%2C%20at%20all%20times%2C%20the%20government%20and%20its%20agencies%20remain%20prepared%20to%20answer%20to%20the%20legitimate%20queries%20of%20the%20people%20whose%20%E2%80%9Cright%20to%20information%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20held%20to%20be%20fundamental%20by%20the%20highest%20court%20in%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coming%20days%20before%20the%20next%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20may%2C%20consequent%20upon%20the%20watershed%20public%20assertion%20of%20March%203%20by%20a%20combined%20opposition%2C%20come%20to%20see%20a%20determined%20bid%20to%20voice%20and%20flesh%20out%20these%20and%20allied%20concerns%20during%20the%20electoral%20campaign%2C%20countering%20the%20so-concerted%20bid%20by%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20to%20peg%20the%20election%20simply%20on%20the%20vacuous%20%E2%80%9Cguarantee%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20cult%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20this%20totalitarian%20attempt%20to%20sink%20real%20issues%20in%20the%20emotive%20miasma%20of%20godlike%20fiat%20must%20be%20challenged%20if%20the%20republic%20is%20to%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20the%203rd%20of%20March%20is%20only%20twelve%20days%20away%20from%20the%20ides%20of%20the%20memorable%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20it%20had%20seemed%20that%20all%20was%20lost%20to%20the%20opposition%20and%2C%20inter-alia%2C%20to%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20voters%2C%20a%20great%20peaceful%2C%20democratic%20change%20may%20be%20in%20the%20offing%2C%20one%20that%20may%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come%20remind%20Caesar%20that%20the%20republic%20is%20still%20alive%20and%20well%2C%20and%20a%20change%20that%20frowns%20upon%20its%20transmogrification%20into%20a%20%C2%A0Presidential%20fiefdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20enable%20Shri%20Modi%20to%20make%20a%20redeemed%20democratic%20bid%20for%20a%20return%20to%20power%20in%202029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20the%20now%20combined%20opposition%20of%202024%20(those%20that%20remain%20undecided%2C%20a%20Mamata%20ji%20or%20a%20Mayawati%20ji%2C%20may%20do%20well%20to%20seize%20the%20moment%20and%20help%20retrieve%20the%20republic)%2C%C2%A0%20the%20least%20false%20step%20induced%20by%20fractious%20cupidity%20can%20still%20cost%20them%20their%20place%20in%20destiny%2C%20most%20likely%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%20to%20come%2C%20if%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20must%20benefit%20from%20the%20old%20adage%3A%20ten%20heads%20are%20better%20than%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fbadri-raina%5C%22%3EBadri%20Raina%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709558941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04181041%2FUntitled-design-26.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliances-patna-rally-is-a-great-political-change-in-the-offing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Close%20to%20a%20million%20citizens%2C%20not%20dumb-driven%2C%20not%20mute%2C%20but%20alive%2C%20astir%2C%20and%20sentient%2C%20packed%20the%20iconic%20Gandhi%C2%A0maidan%20in%20Patna.%22%2C%22author%22%3A