20on%20part%20of%20the%20Rayagada%20train%20crew%20and%20their%20skipping%20a%20red%20signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fandhra-accident-initial-probe-points-finger-at-rayagada-passenger-train-crew%2F1824729%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20preliminary%20investigation%20by%20the%20railways%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20the%20collision%20was%20caused%20by%20the%20Rayagada%20train%20not%20stopping%20at%20and%20then%20slowly%20proceeding%20past%20a%20%E2%80%98defective%E2%80%99%20automatic%20signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20crew%20members%20died%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EV.%20Balachandran%2C%20who%20as%20of%20October%20was%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Loco%20Running%20Staff%20Association%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20association%20had%20written%20to%20the%20railways%20days%20before%20the%20accident%20about%20the%20auto%20signalling%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20the%20association%20said%20that%20train%20crews%20needed%20%E2%80%9Cintensive%20training%E2%80%9D%20to%20become%20familiar%20with%20the%20auto%20signalling%20system%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20newly%20commissioned%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20a%20newly%20introduced%20system%2C%20repeated%20representations%20were%20given%20to%20the%20authorities%20concerned%2C%20including%20the%20General%20Manager%2C%20Divisional%20Railway%20manager%20and%20others%2C%20requesting%20to%20impart%20intensive%20training%20for%20Loco%20Pilots%20and%20Assistant%20Loco%20Pilots%20to%20understand%20the%20working%20of%20the%20signals%20%E2%80%A6%20but%20it%20was%20never%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Finitial-probe-blames-crew-faulty-signal-for-train-tragedy%2Farticle67481127.ece%5C%22%3EBalachandran%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20newspaper%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp