-text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa%3D%5C%22block-kit-renderer%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20this%20%E2%80%98clarification%E2%80%99%20too%20has%20the%20government%20tangled%20in%20knots.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20line%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprocess%20of%20seeking%20permission%20%2C%20labelling%20%26amp%3B%20consent%20based%20disclosure%20to%20user%20abt%20untested%20platforms%20is%20insurance%20policy%20to%20platforms%20who%20can%20otherwise%20be%20sued%20by%20consumers%E2%80%9D%20has%20led%20people%20in%20the%20tech%20space%20to%20ask%20as%20to%20how%20the%20government%20provide%20insurance%20to%20private%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThank%20you%20for%20the%20clarification.%20How%20can%20GoI%20provide%20insurance%20for%20a%20private%20action%20between%20parties%3F%20State%20can%20pay%20no%20role%20in%20a%20private%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mishi%20Choudhary%20(%40MishiChoudhary)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMishiChoudhary%2Fstatus%2F1764545504174584265%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnger%20over%20Knee-Jerk%20%E2%80%98Advisory%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBindu%20Reddy%2C%20CEO%20of%20AbacusAI%2C%20which%20uses%20%E2%80%9CGen%20AI%20to%20build%20Applied%20AI%20and%20LLM%20agents%20and%20systems%20at%20scale%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fbindureddy%2Fstatus%2F1764416727281287380%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20just%20kissed%20its%20future%20goodbye!%20Every%20company%20deploying%20a%20GenAI%20model%20now%20requires%20approval%20from%20the%20Indian%20government!%20That%20is%2C%20you%20now%20need%20approval%20for%20merely%20deploying%20a%207b%20open-source%20model.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReddy%20spoke%20of%20perils%20of%20applications%20in%20triplicate%20but%20importantly%2C%20underlining%20how%20exercising%20control%20like%20this%20could%20allow%20other%20local%20monopolies%20to%20grow.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20know%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20you%20know%20this%20will%20a%20huge%20drag!%20All%20forms%20will%20need%20to%20completed%20in%20triplicate%20and%20there%20will%20be%20a%20dozen%20hoops%20to%20jump%20through!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20This%20is%20how%20monopolies%20thrive%2C%20countries%20decay%20and%20consumers%20suffer!%20Sadly%20India%20is%20already%20dominated%20by%20monopolies%2C%20nepotism%20and%20bureaucracy%20and%20this%20new%20rule%20just%20made%20it%20far%20worse.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20as%20a%20capital%20for%20crony%20capitalism%20has%20been%20soaring.%20In%20May%20last%20year%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Economist%3C%2Fem%3E%20named%20Russia%20and%20India%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqz.com%2Frussia-and-india-among-top-crony-capitalist-countries-1850418002%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emost%20crony%20capitalist%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Monopoly%20of%20Reliance%20across%20media%2C%20on%20data%2C%20via%20Jio%20and%20now%20potentially%20in%20the%20world%20of%20infotainment%20after%20tying%20up%20with%20Walt%20Disney%20is%20ringing%20alarm%20bells.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETechcrunch%20has%20reported%20that%20while%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20IT%20issued%20the%20advisory%20to%20firms%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20advisory%2C%20has%20not%20been%20published%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20TechCrunch%20has%20reviewed%2C%E2%80%9D%20also%20asks%20tech%20firms%20to%20ensure%20that%20their%20services%20or%20products%20%E2%80%9Cdo%20not%20permit%20any%20bias%20or%20discrimination%20or%20threaten%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process.%E2%80%9D%20Techcrunch%20says%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmany%20Indian%20startups%20and%20VCs%20say%20they%20have%20been%20spooked%20by%20the%20new%20advisory%20and%20believe%20such%20regulation%20will%20hinder%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20global%20race%2C%20where%20it%20is%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F05%2F03%2Fwhere-is-india-in-the-generative-ai-race%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealready%20lagging%20behind%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20cites%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchheplo%2Fstatus%2F1764434029838037271%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPratik%20Desai%2C%20founder%20of%20startup%20Kisan%20AI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20such%20a%20fool%20thinking%20I%20will%20work%20bringing%20Gen%20AI%20to%20Indian%20agriculture%20from%20SF%2C%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20training%20multimodal%20low%20cost%20pest%20and%20disease%20model%2C%20and%20so%20excited%20about%20it.%20This%20is%20terrible%20and%20demotivating%20after%20working%204yrs%20full%20time%20brining%20AI%20to%20this%20domain%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20Silicon%20Valley%20leaders%20have%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20what%20the%20portal%20terms%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20policy%20shift.%E2%80%9D%20Aravind%20Srinivas%2C%20co-founder%20and%20chief%20executive%20of%20Perplexity%20AI%2C%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20AI%20start-ups%2C%20said%20the%20new%20advisory%20from%20New%20Delhi%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAravSrinivas%2Fstatus%2F1764429686787252402%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebad%20move%20by%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMartin%20Casado%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20venture%20firm%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%2C%20is%20qu